<section class="section testimonials">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title text-center mb-8">What People Are Saying</h2>
    
    <div class="testimonial-grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-content">
          <p>"RehabRate helped me find a treatment center that actually understood my needs. The reviews were spot-on and I'm now 18 months sober thanks to making the right choice."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar"></div>
          <div class="testimonial-info">
            <h4>Michael T.</h4>
            <p>Recovery success story</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-content">
          <p>"After trying two centers that weren't right for my sister, we used RehabRate to find a center specializing in dual diagnosis. The detailed reviews helped us make a more informed decision."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar"></div>
          <div class="testimonial-info">
            <h4>Jennifer L.</h4>
            <p>Family member</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="testimonial-content">
          <p>"As a treatment provider, RehabRate gives us valuable feedback from patients that helps us continuously improve our programs. The verification process ensures all reviews are legitimate."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar"></div>
          <div class="testimonial-info">
            <h4>Dr. Sarah M.</h4>
            <p>Treatment center director</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials {
    background-color: #f0f9ff;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .testimonial-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .testimonial-card {
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  
  .testimonial-content {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .testimonial-content p {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .testimonial-avatar {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: #e1e1e1;
    margin-right: 1rem;
  }
  
  .testimonial-info h4 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  
  .testimonial-info p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .testimonial-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>